She looked at Quickstrike, shaking a little.  She looked at the body 
she had stepped on. She looked back at Quickstrike,"I..I stepped on 
one of them. I...it.."  She looked at him with a frown. "I'm sorry. 
I'n overly jumpy right now.  Sorry."  She looked down walked quickly 
past Quickstrike.  Slightly embarrest at herself.  She wasn't happy 
that a warrior like herself was, well, acting silly.  She stood a few 
feet away in a darker corner, the shakes had returned ad she would 
have to wait them out for a few moments untill they past.
